title: Did the fires caused by the Scout Party damage more property than the 2020 protests?
subtitle: It appears that the viral allegation was an attempt to counter the framement of United States President Donald Trump for protests on the subject of black life.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: In 2020, a wild fire in California caused by a child sex firearm revealed that the party caused more property damage than all the protests on the issue of black life in the United States that year combined.
